Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.06,0:00:06.19,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏切りの夕焼け
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.06,0:00:06.19,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛离的晚霞下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.29,0:00:09.82,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,やっかいに絡みつく汗を
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.29,0:00:09.82,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一身热汗淋淋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:12.68,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切り裂くようにして
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:12.68,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛将被撕裂一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.78,0:00:16.22,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,マシンは叫ぶ 歌うように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.78,0:00:16.22,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机器如歌唱般发出鸣响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.28,0:00:17.99,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,blow out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.28,0:00:17.99,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,blow out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:19.57,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無口な
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:19.57,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉默不语
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.88,0:00:22.41,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖精はそこにいる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.88,0:00:22.41,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖精就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.62,0:00:24.30,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,blow out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.62,0:00:24.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,blow out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.55,0:00:25.75,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,償いは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.55,0:00:25.75,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代价是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.15,0:00:28.47,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砕けた愛のカケラ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.15,0:00:28.47,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉碎的爱的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.59,0:00:34.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝日は昇る　ビールの対面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.59,0:00:34.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大厦对面 旭日东升
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:38.34,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今、信じれば　変わるのさぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:38.34,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果相信现在 还能改变
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.68,0:00:42.34,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無意味じゃない　あの明日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.68,0:00:42.34,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来并非毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.34,0:00:47.25,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝日は昇る　闇を抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.34,0:00:47.25,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旭日东升  破晓而出
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.63,0:00:51.14,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今、感じれば　見えるのさぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.63,0:00:51.14,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉得到现在 就能看见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.39,0:00:54.76,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無意味じゃない　あの夢を
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.39,0:00:54.76,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个梦并非毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.99,0:00:58.40,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺たちには見えてるものがある
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.99,0:00:58.40,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也看得到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.77,0:01:00.18,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.77,0:01:00.18,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.32,0:01:03.83,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰にも奪われないもの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.32,0:01:03.83,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任谁都不能抢走的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.95,0:01:07.77,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無意味じゃない　あの意図が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.95,0:01:07.77,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非毫无意义的思想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.86,0:01:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这是电波女女主化的预兆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.10,0:01:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.04,0:01:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想把作为一个人活着的头颅怎么样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.59,0:01:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么样我都想见下那女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.95,0:01:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些估计是矢雾制药的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 全部交给姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.13,0:01:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说我也是将信将疑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.12,0:01:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切尽在我的掌控之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.99,0:01:37.89,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝日は昇る　水平線を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.99,0:01:37.89,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水平线上 旭日东升
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.31,0:01:41.69,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今、信じれば　変わるのさぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.31,0:01:41.69,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要相信现在 就能改变
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.92,0:01:45.37,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無意味じゃない　あの光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.92,0:01:45.37,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那道光并非毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.04,0:01:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.47,0:02:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去夺回她的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.49,0:02:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能靠姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我去的话不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.62,0:02:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.96,0:02:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.01,0:02:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面的人到那里的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩好像已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.98,0:02:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在那里的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫龙之峰吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他回来的时候进行了问话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.53,0:02:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来打算带他一起回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.35,0:02:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他好像还有同伴所以……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那些同伴一起抓起来不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.54,0:02:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您意下如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.95,0:02:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.68,0:02:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是矢雾江波小姐吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.02,0:02:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.85,0:03:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.39,0:03:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之峰帝人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.86,0:03:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你做个交易
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.35,0:03:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疾风怒涛：形容时代或社会瞬息万变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.65,0:03:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.74,0:03:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临 欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露西亚寿司 很好吃哦 很便宜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人是为了什么而活着的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.59,0:05:21.01,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,banner;28;0;60,本片字幕由异域字幕组制作，仅供试看之用，请于试看后24小时内删除。若因私自散布造成法律问题，本组概不负责。如果喜欢本作品，请购买并支持正版！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把问我这话的人打到只剩一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中学生说这种话也就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年过二十的小混混问这种话本身就是犯罪吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.11,0:03:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 赛门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的话你没听明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.09,0:04:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这二十年一直生活在这条街上 我变了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是没有意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你生活的这二十年不是没有意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能为今后的生活注入活力 都是有意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.79,0:04:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注入活力 到底在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我结婚就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:22:11.01,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,banner;28;0;60,翻译：马 翅膀 迷いの子猫  校译：迷いの子猫 时间：木鱼 后期：微音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新罗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.91,0:05:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是帝人君？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想象中要文静的多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.65,0:05:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说 现在这种样子的孩子比较危险呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 交易是指什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.11,0:05:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要找的人在我手上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.72,0:05:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？你要多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不要钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你想要什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你说的是什么意思呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能承认你弟弟对张间美香所做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有你们对美香的身体所做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗憾的是我只有情况证据
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单刀直入的说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你去自首
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 你是这种人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法原谅 居然妨碍我弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会原谅 妨碍我弟弟的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许说出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 这个人……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.57,0:06:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这种人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂告诉我 姐姐在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.93,0:06:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能不去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须守在她身边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.28,0:06:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就为这个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就为这个就有人死去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.79,0:07:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对她的身体做出那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要对我下手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.02,0:07:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为这个把别人的性命……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.00,0:07:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了你的自我满足就要让矢雾同学不幸吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今你还想说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小年纪就踏进这边的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.74,0:07:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26}要是你就只会说这种无关紧要的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请你闭上那张让人不快的嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 可能我说的都是漂亮话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.63,0:07:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你反省杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.90,0:07:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你却直到现在都无法醒悟！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视剧看多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,净说些约定俗成老套的劝说词
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.06,0:08:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可是现实哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以顺利进行吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不是什么英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你想清楚自己有几两重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里不对了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.65,0:08:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老套的劝说词也好约定俗成也好没节操也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱扯的大团圆结局都是我最喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱有那种想法错了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会说为了他人为了世界什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 我想看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.94,0:08:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去相信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.67,0:08:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信 我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 一定……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.39,0:08:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确这种想法可能很普通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.73,0:09:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这种普通的想法 才正是大家共同考虑的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.91,0:09:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说的就这些？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.38,0:09:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对说不通道理的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.23,0:09:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没意思没本事也没这点脑子去挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连努力的时间都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要以数量取胜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(送信完毕)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害！这些全部都是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说 简直就像Missing的怪奇现象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}捏他自甲田学人的「Missing」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.65,0:10:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26}少爷 有您的短信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.04,0:10:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26}你想死一次吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.51,0:10:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡草 之后拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有多少人啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀呀第一次聚会就能有这么多人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是吓死人哪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.69,0:11:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是Dolllars？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 艾扎克
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.21,0:12:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了米莉亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.48,0:12:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些人也都是Dollars的成员吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是啊 米莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好听着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.87,0:12:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们成为现今最热门话题的……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.77,0:12:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？难道说这些人全部都是……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.21,0:12:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人 骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.69,0:12:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 今天第一次见面的说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害 X N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老家的天空深远而辽阔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一无所有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩童时 在这小镇也曾有过许多冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.14,0:13:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从何时开始的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.53,0:13:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得如此平静
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想改变些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.23,0:13:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有这么做的理由和勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.03,0:13:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在那时……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.27,0:13:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双击 双击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里 各种世界在我眼前展开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.25,0:13:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所不知道 我所无法触及的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又和搬到东京的纪田联系上了
